trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CodeSubDirectory"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en mängd <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CodeSubDirectory"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: The CodeSubDirectoriesCollection defines an ordered collection of subdirectories containing files compiled at run time.
trans-unit.target: CodeSubDirectoriesCollection definierar en ordnad samling underkataloger som innehåller filer som kompileras under körning.

trans-unit.source: You can have any number of subdirectories.
trans-unit.target: Du kan ha valfritt antal underkataloger.

trans-unit.source: This collection refers to the `codeSubDirectories` element of the `compilation` section of the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Den här samlingen refererar till den `codeSubDirectories` element i den `compilation` avsnittet i konfigurationsfilen.

trans-unit.source: The collection will only provide the items defined in the root Web.config or higher.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen får bara objekten som definierats i Web.config-roten eller högre.

trans-unit.source: This collection is a construct that allows easy access to the compilation information it contains.
trans-unit.target: Den här samlingen är en konstruktion som ger enkel åtkomst till Kompileringsinformation som den innehåller.
